stood to reason that if dairy farmers stay healthy they might be 
able to afford to buy computer software programs to manage herds 
she said she had no idea of coelhos investment at the time 
one argument for exempting congress from conflictofinterest 
statutes is that lawmakers must publicly disclose their holdings so 
voters can decide whether an official is acting for personal 
enrichment 
coelho listed his holding as dairy management associates in 1983 
