the peoples liberation army caught in 
transition between revolutionary force and modern army has been 
thrust into a key role in the standoff between the government and 
prodemocracy students 
as time passed and the governmentordered suppression of the 
monthlong student revolt failed to materialize the pla appeared 
illprepared or reluctant to carry out its mission 
young soldiers waiting in convoys on the outskirts of the 
